Link Object

Link.Rd

Link Object

Usage

Link(url = NULL, relativeLink = NULL, pageObjectId = NULL, slideIndex = NULL)

Arguments

url

(string) If set, indicates this is a link to the external web page at this URL.

relativeLink

(string) If set, indicates this is a link to a slide in this presentation, addressed by its position.

  • RELATIVE_SLIDE_LINK_UNSPECIFIED: An unspecified relative slide link.

  • NEXT_SLIDE: A link to the next slide.

  • PREVIOUS_SLIDE: A link to the previous slide.

  • FIRST_SLIDE: A link to the first slide in the presentation.

  • LAST_SLIDE: A link to the last slide in the presentation.

pageObjectId

(string) If set, indicates this is a link to the specific page in this presentation with this ID. A page with this ID may not exist.

slideIndex

(integer) If set, indicates this is a link to the slide at this zero-based index in the presentation. There may not be a slide at this index.

Value

Link object

Details

A hypertext link.
